I don't think it's a great pattern to make 'started' the default case without checking the action.

I suggest something like

```
if (modelFeedMetadata.action == 'published') {
    return 'published';
  } else if (modelFeedMetadata.action == 'destroyed') {
    return 'stopped';
  } else if (modelFeedMetadata.action == 'started') {
    return 'started';
  } else {
    return modelFeedMetadata.action;
```
